Name: Domina
About the game: Take charge of a gladiator school in Ancient Rome & test your strength in lightning-fast, bloody battles of pixels and raunchy insults! Wrangle politicians and win favor from the Gods to achieve victory in the arena! Elevate your family name with success, or starve to death in obscurity and defeat. Domina is a Pixelart Gladiator Management Simulator with Chariot Racing and Twitch Integration, vaguely based on Roman gladiator schools circa {55B.C. - 55A.D.}
